Commands (Ensure you do not forget to amend these commands to suit your needs especially directories):

Kiwix Apps

https://kiwix.org/en/applications/

Kiwix Library

https://library.kiwix.org/#lang=eng

Kiwix Docker Run Command ( https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-tools/blob/main/docker/server/README.md )

docker run -v /tmp/zim:/data -p 8080:8080 ghcr.io/kiwix/kiwix-serve '*.zim'

Winbdows

Download wikipedia in powershell (Change directory to the kiwix dir)

cd C:\Users\keith\Documents\Kiwix

Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://download.kiwix.org/zim/wikipedia/wikipedia_en_all_maxi_2024-01.zim" -OutFile "wikipedia_en_all_maxi_2024-01.zim"

Linux

cd /your/kiwix/folder

wget -c -P /mnt/Storage1/big-bear-kiwix-serve/zim https://download.kiwix.org/zim/wikipedia/wikipedia_en_all_maxi_2025-06.zim

Casa OS

Open terminal top left icon

login with underlying OS username and password

cd /your/kiwix/folder

wget -c -P /mnt/Storage1/big-bear-kiwix-serve/zim https://download.kiwix.org/zim/wikipedia/wikipedia_en_all_maxi_2025-06.zim
